Ko te Times Amashuri Makuru (THE), i mua ko te Times Amashuri Makuru Yongeyeho (THES), we moheni Ingarangi e whakaatu ana i nga korero me nga gufata e pa ana ki te maatauranga teitei.

== Nyirubwite ==
TPG Capital yaguze uburezi bwa TSL muri Charterhouse mu masezerano miliyoni 400 zama pound muri Nyakanga 2013 maze ihindura TSL Education, muri yo Amashuri Makuru ayigiramo uruhare, nka TES Global. Kugura kwa TPG byagaragaje impinduka ya gatatu nyir'ubwite mu gihe kitarenze imyaka icumi ya Times Higher Education, yari isanzwe ifitwe na News International mbere yo kugurwa na Exponent Private Equity mu 2005.

Muri Werurwe 2019, itsinda ryigenga ryigenga Inflexion Pvt. Equity Partners LLP yaguze Times Amashuri Makuru muri TPG Capital, ibaye ba nyirayo ba kane mumyaka 15. Nyuma yo kugurwa nitsinda ryigenga ryigenga, Times Higher Education yakozwe nkikigo cyigenga kuva TES Global. Ishoramari ryakozwe na Inflexion yihariye yo kugura isoko ryo hagati.

Umujyanama wihariye wo kugura na Inflexion ni Houlihan Lokey, isosiyete ishora imari yafashije mbere amatsinda menshi y’abikorera ku giti cyabo kubona amashyirahamwe y’uburezi yunguka. Nyuma yo kugura, Houlihan Lokey yavuze ko itsinda ry’Amashuri Makuru risanzwe rizakora kugira ngo rihuze ibyifuzo by’ibicuruzwa n’ibicuruzwa, kandi harebwe no kugurisha abakiriya bahari.

== Amateka ==
Kuva ku nomero yacyo ya mbere, mu 1971, kugeza mu 2008, The Times Higher Education Supplement (THES) yasohotse mu buryo bw'ikinyamakuru kandi yavutse, kandi ifatanya n'ikinyamakuru The Times. Ku ya 10 Mutarama 2008, yasubukuwe nk'ikinyamakuru. Yasohowe na TES Global, kugeza mu Kwakira 2005 yari igabana rya News International Rupert Murdoch. Ikinyamakuru cyateguwe na John Gill. Phil Baty ni umwanditsi mukuru, kandi ashinzwe gukwirakwiza mpuzamahanga. Ni n'umwanditsi w'ikinyamakuru World University Rankings.

Iki kinyamakuru kirimo inkingi mpimbano yanditswe na Laurie Taylor, "Poppletonian", igaragaza ubuzima muri kaminuza ya Poppleton.

Mu mwaka wa 2011, Times Higher Education yahawe igihembo cyiswe "Ikinyamakuru cy’ubucuruzi cy’icyumweru" na "Media Business Brand of the Year" n’ishyirahamwe ry’abanditsi babigize umwuga.

Muri 2019, byavuzwe cyane ko Elsevier usanzwe akorana na THE mu rwego rwo gukusanya urutonde rwabo muri kaminuza, yateganyaga kwigarurira Times Higher Education burundu.

Muri Kanama 2020, Times Higher Education yatangaje ubufatanye n’ikigo gishinzwe gushaka abakozi SI-UK hamwe n’umushinga w’amacumbi Casita, byerekana ko cyinjiye mu kwinjiza abanyeshuri mu mahanga no ku masoko y’imiturire y’abanyeshuri.

Ku ya 11 Nzeri 2020, Studyportals ikorera mu Buholandi yatangaje ko yagiranye amasezerano na Times Higher Education, izasura abanyeshuri basura urubuga rwa Times Higher Education berekeje ku rubuga rw’abanyeshuri ba Studyportals igihe cyose abanyeshuri bareba amasomo ayobowe na kaminuza THE THE iri mu Urutonde rwa Kaminuza Yisi.

